    "name": "Poll Manager API",
    "description": "REST Collection for the poll_manager module in Drupal.\n\n**Authentication:** HTTP Basic Auth — user `admin`, password `admin`.\n\n**Variables:**\n- `base_url` — Lando base URL (e.g., `http://simplevoting.lndo.site`)\n- `uuid` — UUID of a Poll Question.\n\nUpdate `base_url` with the port displayed by `lando start`.",
